    "For an example of this approach, see Snippe et al. (2021), and for a subsequent application, see Snippe et al. (2023).",
    "Like the multiple theory approach, this approach still requires that choices need to be made about whether and how to integrate into one DCT specification or multiple DCT specifications.",
